# Emirates Booking App ✈️

A simple flight booking web application built using **Java**, **Spring Boot**, and **MySQL**.  
It simulates basic airline ticket booking with clean code separation using MVC architecture.

---

## 🔧 Features

- User-friendly booking interface (HTML-based)
- RESTful API integration using Spring Boot
- Booking records stored in MySQL database
- Organized into Model, Controller, Service, and Repository layers
- Tested using Postman

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Java 11  
- Spring Boot  
- MySQL  
- HTML, CSS  
- Postman  
- GitHub (for version control)

